*emacs-23.3_rc1 (01 Mar 2011)

  01 Mar 2011; Ulrich Mueller <ulm@gentoo.org> +emacs-23.3_rc1.ebuild,
  metadata.xml:
  Version bump. The sound USE flag is global now.

  02 Feb 2011; Ulrich Mueller <ulm@gentoo.org> emacs-22.3-r7.ebuild,
  emacs-23.2-r3.ebuild:
