*emacs-23.2-r3 (30 Jan 2011)
*emacs-22.3-r7 (30 Jan 2011)
*emacs-21.4-r23 (30 Jan 2011)

  30 Jan 2011; Ulrich Mueller <ulm@gentoo.org> +emacs-21.4-r23.ebuild,
  +emacs-22.3-r7.ebuild, +emacs-23.2-r3.ebuild:
  Apply changes from prefix overlay and from bug 268793. Thanks to Matsui
  Tetsushi <VED03370@nifty.ne.jp> and Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org>.
  Respect the --with-crt-dir configure option also on 32 bit architectures,
  fixes bug 350532. Remove unnecessary automake dependency. Don't compress
  GNU Info dir. Update ebuilds to EAPI 4, for docompress and REQUIRED_USE.

  29 Dec 2010; Ulrich Mueller <ulm@gentoo.org> emacs-22.3-r6.ebuild,
  emacs-23.2-r2.ebuild:
  Don't hardcode user for game score files.

